:"d8996f035d8fed1e573151f9da0344465fecf020","tid":1095470,"uid":136582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"493c4aaaf7fbd15c1d6e66c2841684b7fbe766c7","tid":1095470,"uid":76524,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:04:10.000Z","msg":"到目前為止<br />\n表白親都係想追/臨追到一半先發現佢有另一半<br />\n所謂唔想令自己痛苦<br />\n直接放低句「Sorry鍾意左你，但唔會再打擾你」<br />\n跟住就無再聯絡咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00:23:29.000Z","msg":"好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲女有仔又唔講 真係唔知為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b34be4a84109bd6fe98f6663b77eb13c3339353","tid":1095470,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"上堂送花"},{"pid":"4a4e86aeff9527145a7529ca07d3bca05f83ac8d","tid":1095470,"uid":136582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a77a8bc067663479b5dcde7404c656dd6e566f1","tid":1095470,"uid":72516,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:17:10.000Z","msg":"大學個陣同宜家既女朋友係同科同學<br />\n有1個學期大家咁岩一齊住宿舍<br />\n日日由朝見到晚，一齊上堂一齊落堂買餸返去煮飯仔<br />\n個時大家都冇拍拖<br />\n但又冇咩進一步既行動<br />\n<br />\n結果之後大家都有大家自己既拖拍<br />\n少左聯絡<br />\n畢業之後大約都係一年至年半先會約到一次食個飯咁<br />\n<br />\n直到上年有一次機緣巧合之下，大家重新聯絡返<br />\n日日都傾msg或者電話，好似大家之間都冇隔膜咁<br />\n直到有一晚約左岀黎，行下傾下，到最後正式我問佢一句可唔可以做我女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家佢已經成為我既未婚妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T00:25:06.000Z","msg":"真係緣份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好sweet"},{"pid":"50287f41a4177dbf1c5b1e3f6b04b740cda85172","tid":1095470,"uid":72516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a4e86aeff9527145a7529ca07d3bca05f83ac8d","tid":1095470,"uid":136582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a77a8bc067663479b5dcde7404c656dd6e566f1","tid":1095470,"u